{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778600229015,"sessionID":"ses_1e33fad9fffeLGycJjlvk3M3DA","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-a27522035271ec09","state":{"status":"error","input":{"command":"Research definitions and references for 8 new terms related to fallopian tube layers","prompt":"Please conduct research to find precise anatomical definitions and scientific references (PMIDs, DOIs, or authoritative sources) for the following 8 terms in the context of the fallopian tube:\n1. mesosalpinx epithelium\n2. antimesosalpinx epithelium\n3. superior epithelium (of the fallopian tube/oviduct)\n4. inferior epithelium (of the fallopian tube/oviduct)\n5. mesosalpinx muscularus\n6. antimesosalpinx muscularus\n7. superior muscularus (of the fallopian tube/oviduct)\n8. inferior muscularus (of the fallopian tube/oviduct)\n\nNote: According to subject matter experts, these terms refer to the polarity/region (mesosalpinx, antimesosalpinx, superior, inferior) within the 'muscle layer of oviduct' and 'mucosa of fallopian tube', but are not necessarily anatomical parts of the 'mesosalpinx' or 'antimesosalpinx' themselves.\n\nFor each term, please provide:\n- A concise anatomical definition.\n- At least one high-quality reference (preferably PMID or DOI).\n- If possible, explain the spatial relationship (polarity) that defines 'mesosalpinx', 'antimesosalpinx', 'superior', and 'inferior' regions of these layers.\n\nPlease present the results in a structured format suitable for ontology term creation.","subagent_type":"general"},"error":"The task tool was called with invalid arguments: SchemaError(Missing key\n  at [\"description\"]).\nPlease rewrite the input so it satisfies the expected schema.","time":{"start":1778600229011,"end":1778600229014}},"id":"prt_e1cd59c7c001uUWHliL5H8cAuG","sessionID":"ses_1e33fad9fffeLGycJjlvk3M3DA","messageID":"msg_e1cd35271001EeLUzHcJLxDxRY"}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1778600229067,"sessionID":"ses_1e33fad9fffeLGycJjlvk3M3DA","part":{"id":"prt_e1cd5b8c8001xZkPslc6lsciuU","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"d3d88c6230a402e5fc7571a9f01d4ca10f345697","messageID":"msg_e1cd35271001EeLUzHcJLxDxRY","sessionID":"ses_1e33fad9fffeLGycJjlvk3M3DA","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":41505,"input":40016,"output":1489,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.0087477}}
